 If there is a designer of our lives like our DNA, 

19
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:22,190
 some people aren't supposed to meet. 

20
00:01:22,190 --> 00:01:27,500
 Meeting each other would mean curse and death. 

21
00:01:28,650 --> 00:01:31,210
 That's why I'm leaving. 

22
